Package org.jlibsedml.modelsupport

A utility package providing services to support specific modelling languages and ontologies used by SED-ML.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BioModelsModelsRetriever
    Class for retreiving SBML models from Biomodels, using a MIRIAM compliant URN
    KisaoOntology
    Singleton class which encapsulates the KISAO ontology.
    KisaoTerm
    Encapsulates a single KISAO term.
    SBMLSupport
    Class to provide general support for working with SBML level 2 and level 3 core models, especially for the construction of XPath strings for use in Change and DataGenerator elements.
    SUPPORTED_LANGUAGE
    Utility class that provides access to some constants describing likely model languages supported by SED-ML.
    ToolSupport
    List of constants useful in this package (model type, simulator type, etc.)
    URLResourceRetriever
    A generic retriever that will return the contents of the specified URI as a URL to an actual resource, and will not validate the URL content.
